**Privacy Policy**

Effective Date: \[11.05.2025]

[chTGPT TO PDF ] respects your privacy. This Chrome extension does **not collect, store, transmit, or share** any personal data or user information.

### Information Collection and Use

This extension operates entirely within your browser and does not collect:

* Personally identifiable information (e.g. name, email, address)
* Health or financial data
* Authentication information (e.g. passwords)
* Web history or user activity
* Any content from the websites you visit

### Permissions

The permissions requested by the extension (e.g. access to active tabs or scripting) are solely used to enable its core functionality and are not used to collect data.

### Third-Party Services

This extension does **not** use any third-party services or remote code that could access user data.

### Changes to This Policy

If changes are made to this policy, an updated version will be made available through the Chrome Web Store listing.

### Contact

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at: smart5translator@gmail.com
